### Create container
POST http://localhost:8082/containers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "image": "nginx:latest",
  "command": [],
  "environment": {
    "ENV_VAR1": "value1",
    "ENV_VAR2": "value2"
  }
}


### Start Container
POST http://localhost:8082/containers/168d21676e9c5e588f7a95ebf2649b18da283626c08fedf54f054f06a32b6794/start

### Stop Container
POST http://localhost:8082/containers/168d21676e9c5e588f7a95ebf2649b18da283626c08fedf54f054f06a32b6794/stop

### Remove Container
POST http://localhost:8082/containers/168d21676e9c5e588f7a95ebf2649b18da283626c08fedf54f054f06a32b6794/remove

### Get Container Status
GET http://localhost:8082/containers/168d21676e9c5e588f7a95ebf2649b18da283626c08fedf54f054f06a32b6794/status



